kpi_info.title: RAB SETUP COMPLETIONS FOR CS DATA CONV
kpi_info.use: The number of RAB setup completions for CS data conversational calls. --- Before this, the RNC has reserved RNC, BTS, and transport resources for the RAB. UPDATED:When the RNC sends an RRC: RADIO BEARER SETUP message, the purpose of which is to establish a radio bearer for a new CS data conversational RAB.
